.zip -mx9 %~f1\\*.* \n7za a -r -tzip %~nx1.zip -mx9 %~f1\\*.* \nrmdir /s/q %~f1\npause\n</pre>\n<p>!!Caution, if you don&#8217;t have 7za installed it will only delete that folder!!</p>\n<p>Usage: </p>\n<p>Drop any directory to the batch file, it will create a zip archive and delete that folder.</p>\n<p>Similarly you can use following batch to just store (uncompressed) your folder:</p>\n<pre>\n@echo offf\necho 7za a -r -tzip %~nx1.zip -mx0 %~f1\\*.* \n7za a -r -tzip %~nx1.zip -mx0 %~f1\\*.* \nrmdir /s/q %~f1\npause\n</pre>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t want to delete your folder just remove <code>rmdir</code> line.</p>\n <div class=\"feedflare\">\n<a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?a=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:yIl2AUoC8zA\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?d=yIl2AUoC8zA\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?a=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:qj6IDK7rITs\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?d=qj6IDK7rITs\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?a=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:-BTjWOF_DHI\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?i=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:-BTjWOF_DHI\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?a=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?i=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:gIN9vFwOqvQ\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?a=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:F7zBnMyn0Lo\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?i=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:F7zBnMyn0Lo\" border=\"0\"></img></a> <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?a=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:V_sGLiPBpWU\"><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/shailan?i=NdM_fwY8QOI:5PLdGXFqpkQ:V_sGLiPBpWU\" border=\"0\"></img></a>\n</div><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/shailan/~4/NdM_fwY8QOI\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" alt=\"\"/>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xm