d desires sanctification for each of His child. Sanctification is an act of separation from that which is evil and of dedication unto God. <em>( Romans 12:1,2; 1 Thessalonians 5:3; Hebrews 13:13 )</em> This can be done by the power of the Lord Jesus Christ.</p>\r\n<p>[/su_tab]</p>\r\n<p>[su_tab title=\"Justification\"]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_tab]</p>\r\n<p>[su_tab title=\"Church\"]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_tab]</p>\r\n<p>[su_tab title=\"Second Coming of the Lord Jesus Christ\"]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_tab]</p>\r\n<p>[su_tab title=\"Biblical and Comprehensive Worship\"]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_tab]</p>\r\n<p>[su_tab title=\"Biblical Praise\"]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_tab]</p>\r\n<p>[su_tab title=\"Divine Healing\"]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_tab]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_tabs]</p>','Doctrinal Statement','','inherit','closed','closed','','368-revision-v1','','','2016-10-05 07:18:31','2016-10-05 07:18:31','',368,'http://localhost/jsos_wp/2016/10/05/368-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(390,1,'2016-10-05 07:21:43','2016-10-05 07:21:43','<p class=\"left-20p bottom-10\">This is intended simply as a basis of fellowship among members of the JSOS Christian Church <em>( \" . . . that we all speak the same things . . . \" –1 Corinthians 1:10 ) .</em> The wordings here are not inspired or contented for but the truth set forth is held to be essential to a full gospel <em>Christian</em> ministry.</p>\r\n<p class=\"bottom-10\">No claim is made that it contains all biblical truths for the obvious reason that this is merely a partial list. Hence, the list may be added upon with supplementary and additional statements in the future.</p>\r\n<p class=\"bottom-30\">However, we strongly believe that this list is Bible-based and is helpful for the identify and growth of the <em>JSOS Christian Church.</em></p>\r\n<p class=\"bottom-30\"> </p>\r\n<p>[su_tabs vertical=\"yes\" class=\"my-custom-tabs\"]<br />\r\n [su_tab title=\"The Bible\"]</p>\r\n<p>We believe in the scripture, both the Old and the New Testament comprising of books to be verbally inspired by 