/p>\r\n<p>[/one_third_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>','Gallery','','publish','closed','closed','','gallery','','','2016-10-20 10:27:51','2016-10-20 10:27:51','',0,'http://localhost/jsos_wp/?page_id=434',0,'page','',0),(435,1,'2016-10-07 04:47:22','2016-10-07 04:47:22','','Photos','','inherit','open','closed','','photos','','','2016-10-07 04:47:46','2016-10-07 04:47:46','',434,'http://localhost/jsos_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/photos.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(436,1,'2016-10-07 04:47:23','2016-10-07 04:47:23','','Songs','','inherit','open','closed','','songs','','','2016-10-07 04:47:52','2016-10-07 04:47:52','',434,'http://localhost/jsos_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/songs.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(437,1,'2016-10-07 04:47:23','2016-10-07 04:47:23','','Videos','','inherit','open','closed','','videos','','','2016-10-07 04:47:58','2016-10-07 04:47:58','',434,'http://localhost/jsos_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/videos.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(438,1,'2016-10-07 04:52:12','2016-10-07 04:52:12','<p>[one_third padding=\"0 20px 0 0\"]</p>\r\n<p><img class=\"size-full wp-image-436 aligncenter\" src=\"http://localhost/jsos_wp/wp-content/uploads/2016/10/songs.jpg\" alt=\"Songs\" width=\"160\" height=\"230\" /></p>\r\n<p class=\"bottom-20\">A collection of<span style=\"color: #800000;\"> <em><strong>JSOS original songs</strong></em> </span>composed by its members. Songs vary from personal to congregational praise and worship songs, fellowship songs, and secular songs. It also features theme songs composed for Christian schools, churches and organizations.</p>\r\n<p class=\"bottom-20\">All sound tracks were arranged and edited by the <em>JSOS Worship Ministry team.</em></p>\r\n<p class=\"bottom-20\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Prayer requests:</em></span> God\'s provision of higher technical trainings and equipments to improve the production and quality of the soundtracks, and to be able to produce our own music album that can minister