lunteers.</p>\r\n<p class=\"bottom-20\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Prayer requests:</em></span>  God\'s provision of high quality video cameras and equipments to improve the overall film production and outputs; God\'s blessings for our church to be able to produce professional short films testifying God\'s greatness; more partners and networks on film making</p>\r\n<p>[/one_third_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>','Gallery','','inherit','closed','closed','','434-revision-v1','','','2016-10-07 05:02:41','2016-10-07 05:02:41','',434,'http://localhost/jsos_wp/2016/10/07/434-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(447,1,'2016-10-07 05:04:27','2016-10-07 05:04:27','<p>[su_animate type=\"fadeInUp\"]<br />\r\n [one_half]</p>\r\n<h3><span style=\"font-size: 40pt;\"><em><span style=\"color: #783614;\"><strong>Purpose Statement</strong></span></em></span></h3>\r\n<hr />\r\n<p>The <strong><em>JSOS Christian Church</em></strong> is committed</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>To bring people to the <em>LORD JESUS CHRIST</em>;</li>\r\n	<li>To lead them to worship and praise <em>GOD</em> in ways that pleases <em>HIM</em>;</li>\r\n	<li>To encourage them to be committed members of <em>GOD\'S</em> family;</li>\r\n	<li>To develop them to <em>CHRIST</em>-like maturity and to equip them;</li>\r\n	<li>To serve <em>GOD</em> and share <em>HIS</em> love to others in the best that they can.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p>[/one_half]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half_last]</p>\r\n<div class=\"left-20\">\r\n<table class=\"jsos-table\">\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><a href=\"http://localhost/jsos_wp/location/\"><br />\r\n</a>\r\n<div class=\"auh auh_location\"> </div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td><a href=\"http://localhost/jsos_wp/history/\"><br />\r\n</a>\r\n<div class=\"auh auh_history\"> </div>\r\n</td>\r\n<td><a href=\"http://localhost/jsos_wp/truth-behind-its-name/\"><br />\r\n</a>\r\n<div class=\"auh auh_truthbehindname\"> </div>\r\n</td>\r\n<!--\r\n\r\n<td><a href=\"#\"><br />\r\n</a>\r\n<div class=\"auh auh_