lor: #993300;\">Biyaya Niya ay kakamtin </span></em><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <em><span style=\"color: #993300;\">\'Pag kasama ay si Kristo </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style=\"color: #993300;\">Ligtas ang buhay mo </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style=\"color: #993300;\">Siya ang moog at sandigan </span></em><br />\r\n <em><span style=\"color: #993300;\">Maasahan kailanman</span></em></p>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>[/two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p> [/su_animate]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_spoiler]</p>\r\n<p>[su_spoiler title=\"RIP (Rest In Praise)\"  class=\"my-custom-spoiler\" style=\"simple\" open=\"no\"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_animate type=\"fadeInUp\"]</p>\r\n<p>[three_fifth padding=\"0 20px 0 0\"]</p>\r\n<p>[su_youtube url=\"http://youtube.com/watch?v=2_MhtAlmzpY\" width=\"480\" height=\"320\"]</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: #993300;\">Composer: <em> <strong>Jhesed </strong><strong>Tacadena<br />\r\n </strong></em></span><span style=\"color: #993300; font-size: 10pt; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><em>Original JSOS Song</em></span></p>\r\n<p>[/three_fifth]<br />\r\n [two_fifth_last]</p>\r\n<p>[one_half]</p>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em><strong>I.</strong> </em></span><br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Napapagod ka na ba? </em></span><br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Sa iyong pagtakbo </em></span><br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Hinihingal ka na ba? </em></span><br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Sundalo ni Kristo </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em><strong>II.</strong> </em></span><br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Nadarama mo ba? </em></span><br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Ang hapdi ng mga sugat </em></span><br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Na nakagugulat, \'di masukat </em></span><br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em>Kahit ika\'y tapat </em></span><br />\r\n <br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000;\"><em><str