to inspire the congregation, through the Holy Spirit, to worship the Lord Jesus with all our heart, with all our soul, with all our mind and with all our strength</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;\"><em><strong>Vision</strong></em></span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>The <em>JSOS Church</em> will become a God-worshiping and praising church - corporately and individually.</li>\r\n	<li>The<em> JSOS Worship Ministry</em> members will manifest the anointing as worship leaders, that through our ministry:\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>People will be convicted by the Holy Spirit to come to Christ and make Him as their Lord and Savior;</li>\r\n	<li>Sicknesses and diseases will be healed by God because of the overwhelming presence and power of the Holy Spirit;</li>\r\n	<li>Spiritually weak and backsliding Christians will be revived and restored.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>The JSOS Worship Team will be actively involved in supporting inter-church activities, such as concert, music fest, etc., that is glorifying to the name of our Lord Jesus Christ.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n	<li>\r\n<h2><span style=\"font-size: 14pt; color: #800000;\"><em><strong>Mission:</strong></em></span></h2>\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Spiritual revival in <em>JSOS</em> in worshipping the Lord Jesus Christ - congregationally and individually.</li>\r\n	<li>Every Worship Ministry member must manifest a worship life that is a level higher than those who are not.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>[/two_third]</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">[one_third_last padding=\"0 20px 0 0\"]<br />\r\n <span style=\"color: #800000; font-size: 14pt;\"><em><strong>Facebook Feed<br />\r\n </strong></em></span>[fts_facebook id=475729819203022 posts=3 posts_displayed=page_only type=page]</p>\r\n<p>[/one_third_last]</p>\r\n<p>[/su_animate]</p>','Praise and Music','','publish','closed','closed','','praise-and-music','','','2016-10-12 07:09:28','2016-10-12 07:09:28','',146,'http://localhost/jso